text: A Force of One is a 1979 American action martial arts movie directed by Paul Aaron and starring Chuck Norris, Jennifer O'Neill, Ron O'Neal, Clu Gulager, Eric Laneuville, James Whitmore Jr, Clint Ritchie, Pepe Serna and Ray Vitte. It was distributed by American Cinema Releasing. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1979 action movies Category:American action movies Category:Movies about police misconduct Category:Martial arts movies
